&quot;You're here to help out in the war too, I see...&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ulatraariah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>LaTra Ariah</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=C:\America Online 6.0\download\moonicon.bmp BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/23/01 2:18:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Healers Hut</span><hr size=1> &quot;And I'm greatful to you both,&quot; She said as she walked up behind Gabrielle and smiled slighlty. &quot;Thank you so much for your help... I'm sorry I couldn't be here sooner to meet you, but I had to take care of an affair with Felicia's daughter.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ualysiaofscynthia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Alysia of Scynthia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 128<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(6/23/01 3:31:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=17.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Healers Hut</span><hr size=1> Alysia smiled lightly at her twin, then turned her attention to Ari.<br>
